"""
SDRG-CMF v5 GeometryGuard Real-World Benchmark with Time-Series Experts

Real-world time-series benchmark comparing:
  - SDRG GeometryGuard online metric-memory model
  - fixed metric baselines
  - RNN / GRU / LSTM / Transformer baselines in PyTorch

Datasets are loaded from statsmodels built-in real-world datasets where possible:
  - Mauna Loa CO2
  - Sunspots
  - Nile river flow
  - US macrodata

Protocol:
  - chronological train/validation/test split
  - scalers fit only on training prefix
  - no future leakage
  - GeometryGuard uses prequential test evaluation:
      predict y_t using train + prior test targets only, then update
  - neural models train on train, tune by validation, evaluate test
  - optional neural online fine-tuning is disabled by default

This is a research benchmark, not a claim of SOTA.
"""

